      <title>格鲁吉亚议会在选举前批准新总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/georgian-parliament-approves-new-premier-ahead-of-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格鲁吉亚立法者在欧盟候选国十月份举行议会选举之前批准伊拉克利·科巴希泽担任新总理。]]></description>
